SELECT project_name, green_area, green_type FROM UrbanDevelopmentProjects JOIN LandUseDataAfter ON UrbanDevelopmentProjects.project_id = LandUseDataAfter.project_id JOIN GreenSpacesAfter ON LandUseDataAfter.land_id = GreenSpacesAfter.land_id WHERE GreenSpacesAfter.green_area > 1000 ORDER BY GreenSpacesAfter.green_area DESC;
